{"title":"泡在北緯11度的周末里，不想上岸","slug":"boracay","date":"2017-11-30T15:38:12.000Z","updated":"2024-04-18T16:18:16.207Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/boracay.json","excerpt":"缘起，来自亚航的一封一如往常的促销邮件，加上对长滩岛的白沙滩和菲律宾的海觊觎已久，算好考试周周末的空档，就决定去了。","covers":["https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/IMG_20171125_125026_362.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-money.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-1.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-2.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-4.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-8.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-9.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-6.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-7.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-5.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-12.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-3.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-10.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-11.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-17.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-18.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-19.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-13.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-14.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-15.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-16.jpg"],"content":"<p>缘起，来自亚航的一封一如往常的促销邮件，加上对长滩岛的白沙滩和菲律宾的海觊觎已久，算好考试周周末的空档，就决定去了。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>在浦东机场准备值机的时候，我就发现被一群中年大妈包围了，原来上海到长滩岛的亚航航班是包机，只有少数票给散客。并不算太漫长的四个小时飞行，一上飞机我就戴着我的sony mdr1000x睡着了，直到快落地被空姐叫醒填入境卡，不得不说降噪耳机在出门旅行的时候简直不要太好用。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/IMG_20171125_125026_362.jpg\" width=\"5440\" height=\"3060\"></p>\n<p>到了kalibo机场，真的是如传说中的一样mini，同时也感受到了来自夏天的问候。换好sim卡和比索，体验了southwest的大巴，转螃蟹船再转小巴的door to door服务，终于到了长滩，简直快要累瘫。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-money.jpg\" width=\"1360\" height=\"907\"></p>\n<p>到了黄昏的时候，换好短袖短裤，踩着洞洞鞋，走到白沙滩等待日落。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-1.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-2.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-4.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\"></p>\n<p>周末第一天一日游出海浮潜，喝了几口海水，咸得像吞了几口盐。</p>\n<!-- <video class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://lvideo.dafork.com/FloVaiFocG20kmmdJJpWQo3yGlcY\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n</video> -->\n<p>长滩岛出名的白沙滩，像面粉一样细而柔软的沙。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-8.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-9.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<!-- <video class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://lvideo.dafork.com/FhLbJx3mM5_wr7hJfJKPJavSNtjB\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n</video> -->\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-6.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-7.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p>之后去魔术岛跳海，先是跳了一个5m的，感觉也没什么，就继续跳了个7m的。</p>\n<!-- <video class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://lvideo.dafork.com/Fltl6Ng0FDli-ipe-pTPMu4GzZwx\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n</video> -->\n<p>晚上从station1到station2沿着海边，一路走走拍拍。后来跟着小伙伴去了长滩岛最大的酒吧，只记得喝了几杯当地的啤酒，后来也上去尬了几次舞，来的大半都是韩国妹子。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-5.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-12.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-3.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-10.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-11.jpg\" width=\"797\" height=\"1200\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-17.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-18.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\"></p>\n<p>周末第二天我们自己玩，到沙滩上当地小黑会用菲式英语问你玩不玩海上项目，这个时候一定要记得砍价，上午我们玩了降落伞，他们会先把你绑在降落伞上，然后在快艇上像放风筝一样升到空中，在海面十几米的上方，长滩岛的风景一览无余。</p>\n<p>周末的尾巴是泡在海里过的，整个下午在沙滩附近的浅海中，游了会泳，学了下冲浪板。东南亚的海对我们貌似都有这样一种魔力，就算过去泡在海里什么都不做，也会觉得买的机票和路上奔波的辛劳都是值得的。</p>\n<p>天快黑的时候决定走之前好好拍个照，于是又是各种蹦啊跳，感觉最近代码写多了，创意稀缺啊。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-19.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-13.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-14.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-15.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-16.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<audio src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=450567505.mp3\" poster=\"http://p2.music.126.net/ZgaAgq6eXTOKHsMU8rYZKA==/109951163909048455.jpg?param=130y130\" name=\"青鸟与诗\" author=\"愚青\" loop autoplay><br></audio>","more":"<p>在浦东机场准备值机的时候，我就发现被一群中年大妈包围了，原来上海到长滩岛的亚航航班是包机，只有少数票给散客。并不算太漫长的四个小时飞行，一上飞机我就戴着我的sony mdr1000x睡着了，直到快落地被空姐叫醒填入境卡，不得不说降噪耳机在出门旅行的时候简直不要太好用。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/IMG_20171125_125026_362.jpg\" width=\"5440\" height=\"3060\"></p>\n<p>到了kalibo机场，真的是如传说中的一样mini，同时也感受到了来自夏天的问候。换好sim卡和比索，体验了southwest的大巴，转螃蟹船再转小巴的door to door服务，终于到了长滩，简直快要累瘫。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinie