ps://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-14.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-15.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/boracay/changtan-16.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\"></p>\n<audio src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=450567505.mp3\" poster=\"http://p2.music.126.net/ZgaAgq6eXTOKHsMU8rYZKA==/109951163909048455.jpg?param=130y130\" name=\"青鸟与诗\" author=\"愚青\" loop autoplay><br></audio>","categories":[{"name":"travel","path":"api/categories/travel.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"海岛","path":"api/tags/海岛.json"},{"name":"菲律宾","path":"api/tags/菲律宾.json"},{"name":"长滩岛","path":"api/tags/长滩岛.json"}]}